overview: In this new mission Commander Lara was entrusted to face TREASON AND CORRUPTION ... In this fight against crime, figuring out the new methods that use the mafia factions to achieve their CRIMES, disguising them with INNOCENCE. It's a movie full of action that will keep you on the edge of suspense from beginning to end, and it will show the methods used by criminal gangs to achieve its objectives in the TRAFFIC OF DOLLARS
title: Dolar Dealers
